--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TIME-MANAGEMENT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Idea:
 - One list on the left or right with all projects.
    - A project can have:
       - Name, description, color.
 - In the list every project have button '+' and '-'.
    - Actions add the project to the overview list on the specific day (or remove
      it).
 - The list have two (or more?) sections.
    - Area automatically ranged, out of scored.
 - The area 'Automatically ranged' ordered automatically the projects depends on 
   there used. Projects which will used more are open, project lesser are more 
   down.
    - Also the user can order the projects manually.
 - In the area 'Out of Score' the projects can manually ordered, but no 
   automatically order will happen.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VIEW
Left side:
 - Available projectlist

Center (right)
 - DayView (this day)
 - WeekView (last 7 days)
 - MonthView (last 30 days)
 - HalfYearView (last 180 days)

